  "Call this site’s live mock endpoint": "Ita sehemu ya huduma ya majaribio ya moja kwa moja ya tovuti hii",
  "Can AI learn from this? To what depth, for which uses, with what obligations?": "Je, AI inaweza kujifunza kutoka hapa? Kwa kina gani, kwa matumizi gani, na wajibu gani?",
