  "Code & schemas — MIT": "Msimbo na schema — MIT",
  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "Mifano ya msimbo, JSON Schemas, na violezo vya sera vinavyosomeka na mashine vina leseni ya MIT isipokuwa imeelezwa vinginevyo. Unaweza kuvitumia katika tovuti zako mwenyewe kwa uhuru.",
  "Combined rights entry point": "Mahali pa pamoja pa kuingilia haki",
