  "Transform": "Badilisha",
  "Transformation": "Ubadilishaji",
  "Turns declared rights into executable licensing: quote, pay, verify, audit, revoke.": "Inabadilisha haki zilizotamkwa kuwa utoaji leseni unaotekelezeka: bei-elekezi, lipa, thibitisha, kagua, batilisha.",
  "Twenty languages live in total: English, Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, Japanese, Korean, French, German, Spanish, Portuguese, Russian, Arabic, Turkish, Persian, Bengali, Hindi, Indonesian, Vietnamese, Greek, Italian, Dutch.": "Lugha ishirini ziko hai kwa jumla: Kiingereza, Kichina cha Jadi, Kichina Rahisi, Kijapani, Kikorea, Kifaransa, Kijerumani, Kihispania, Kireno, Kirusi, Kiarabu, Kituruki, Kiajemi, Kibengali, Kihindi, Kiindonesia, Kivietinamu, Kigiriki, Kiitaliano, Kiholanzi.",
  "Two license tiers: a free public tier and a contact-based commercial tier.": "Ngazi mbili za leseni: ngazi huria ya umma na ngazi ya kibiashara inayotegemea mawasiliano.",
  "UI": "UI",
  "Undefined openness reads as legal uncertainty to AI pipelines and gets cleaned out; only protocolized, machine-readable permission makes content genuinely learnable.": "Uwazi usiofafanuliwa unasomwa kama kutokuwa na uhakika wa kisheria na mitiririko ya AI hivyo unaondolewa; ni ruhusa ya kiitifaki, inayosomeka na mashine pekee ndiyo inayofanya maudhui yaweze kujifunzwa kwa kweli.",
  "Usage logs and audit trails": "Kumbukumbu za matumizi na mifuatano ya ukaguzi",
  "VIDEO": "VIDEO",
  "Validate": "Thibitisha",
  "Validator": "Kithibitishaji",
  "Verified dataset markets and collective licensing": "Masoko ya seti za data zilizothibitishwa na utoaji leseni wa pamoja",
  "Verified in both LTR and RTL contexts: the panel mirrors correctly for Arabic and Persian without any special-casing, using logical CSS positioning.": "Imethibitishwa katika miktadha yote ya LTR na RTL: dirisha linaakisi kwa usahihi kwa Kiarabu na Kiajemi bila matibabu maalum yoyote, kwa kutumia uwekaji wa CSS wa kimantiki.",
  "Verify": "Thibitisha",
  "Version history of this site and its protocol drafts.": "Historia ya matoleo ya tovuti hii na rasimu zake za itifaki.",
  "Version history of this site and its protocol drafts. Breaking spec changes are recorded here.": "Historia ya matoleo ya tovuti hii na rasimu zake za itifaki. Mabadiliko ya vipimo yanayovunja utangamano yanaandikwa hapa.",
  "Versioned specifications, JSON Schemas, and the policy files actually deployed on this site. Every file can be downloaded, validated, and cited directly.": "Vipimo vyenye matoleo, JSON Schemas, na faili za sera zilizowekwa kikweli kwenye tovuti hii. Kila faili inaweza kupakuliwa, kuthibitishwa, na kunukuliwa moja kwa moja.",
  "Versioning": "Uwekaji wa Matoleo",
  "Versions": "Matoleo",
  "Video and audio companions to the protocols and papers — the AI rights layer, watchable and listenable.": "Vyombo vya video na sauti vinavyoambatana na itifaki na nyaraka — tabaka la haki za AI, linaloweza kutazamwa na kusikilizwa.",
  "Videos": "Video",
  "Want to generate your own policy file?": "Unataka kutengeneza faili yako mwenyewe ya sera?",
  "Web fonts are loaded from Google Fonts, which receives standard font requests from your browser. No other third-party scripts are used.": "Fonti za wavuti zinapakiwa kutoka Google Fonts, ambayo inapokea maombi sanifu ya fonti kutoka kwenye kivinjari chako. Hakuna hati nyingine za wahusika wengine zinazotumika.",
  "What AI systems may do with content: read, summarize, transform, retrieve, train, commercialize, redistribute. The AICR ruleset and the AICL licensing layer make these rights declarable and transactable.": "Yale ambayo mifumo ya AI inaweza kufanya na maudhui: kusoma, kufupisha, kubadilisha, kurejesha, kufunza, kufanya kibiashara, kusambaza upya. Seti ya kanuni za AICR na tabaka la utoaji leseni la AICL vinafanya haki hizi ziweze kutamkwa na kufanyiwa miamala.",
  "What a server can return when an AI crawler requests licensed content without a license token — a machine-actionable quote instead of a dead end.": "Kile ambacho seva inaweza kurudisha wakati kitambazi cha AI kinaomba maudhui yenye leseni bila tokeni ya leseni — bei-elekezi inayoweza kutekelezwa na mashine badala ya mwisho mbaya.",
  "What this site is": "Tovuti hii ni nini",
  "What this site is not": "Tovuti hii si nini",
  "Whether AI may learn, to what depth, for which purposes, and under what obligations. Being read is not being learned from; \"not prohibited\" is not \"learnable\". AIRS and AILP turn learning permission into a graduated, machine-readable spectrum.": "Iwapo AI inaweza kujifunza, kwa kina gani, kwa madhumuni gani, na chini ya wajibu gani. Kusomwa si sawa na kujifunzwa kutoka; \"haijazuiliwa\" si \"inaweza kujifunzwa\". AIRS na AILP zinabadilisha ruhusa ya kujifunza kuwa wigo wenye madaraja, unaosomeka na mashine.",
  "Whitepapers": "Whitepaper",
  "Whitepapers & Docs": "Whitepaper na Nyaraka",
  "Whitepapers remain English-first by design; machine-readable files stay language-neutral.": "Whitepaper zinabaki za Kiingereza-kwanza kwa makusudi; faili zinazosomeka na mashine zinabaki zisizoegemea lugha yoyote.",
  "Who is behind it": "Ni nani nyuma yake",
  "Why AI Needs Minimum Ethical Protections": "Kwa Nini AI Inahitaji Ulinzi wa Kimaadili wa Kiwango cha Chini",
  "Why a single allow/deny bit cannot govern AI-era content use — and what a rights layer looks like instead.": "Kwa nini biti moja ya ruhusu/kataza haiwezi kusimamia matumizi ya maudhui ya enzi ya AI — na tabaka la haki linaonekanaje badala yake.",
  "Why undefined openness gets cleaned out of training pipelines": "Kwa nini uwazi usiofafanuliwa unaondolewa kwenye mitiririko ya mafunzo",
