  "each level independently licensable & auditable": "kila ngazi ina uwezekano wa kupewa leseni na kukaguliwa kivyake",
  "embedding — vectorization and retrieval indexes": "embedding — uvekta na faharasa za urejeshaji",
  "found": "imepatikana",
  "i18n": "i18n",
  "in-browser + live API": "ndani ya kivinjari + API ya moja kwa moja",
  "inference_input — use as context at inference time (RAG)": "inference_input — matumizi kama muktadha wakati wa uzalishaji (RAG)",
