  "quotation — excerpt limits and attribution rules": "quotation — mipaka ya dondoo na kanuni za utambulisho wa chanzo",
  "rag_use — retrieval-augmented generation, retention windows": "rag_use — uzalishaji ulioongezwa kwa urejeshaji, vipindi vya uhifadhi",
  "read_access — whether AI may fetch and read the content": "read_access — iwapo AI inaweza kupakua na kusoma maudhui",
  "redistribution — republishing or redistributing content or derivatives": "redistribution — kuchapisha upya au kusambaza upya maudhui au yatokanayo nayo",
  "research pages & whitepapers": "kurasa za utafiti na whitepaper",
  "robots.txt and llms.txt govern access and visibility, not learning depth or use permissions. AIRS proposes expressing AI rights as a proportional, use-specific spectrum across ten dimensions — access, indexing, inference input, embedding, training, fine-tuning, distillation, memory, output, attribution/compensation. AILP translates this into /ai/rights-spectrum.json, letting creators declare granular permissions with compensation models ranging from free through license-required to revenue share.": "robots.txt na llms.txt vinasimamia ufikiaji na uonekanaji, si kina cha kujifunza au ruhusa za matumizi. AIRS inapendekeza kueleza haki za AI kama wigo sawia, mahususi kwa matumizi, katika vipimo kumi — ufikiaji, uorodheshaji, ingizo la muktadha, embedding, mafunzo, kurekebisha, uyeyushaji, kumbukumbu, matokeo, utambulisho wa chanzo/fidia. AILP inabadilisha hili kuwa /ai/rights-spectrum.json, ikiruhusu waundaji kutamka ruhusa za kina kwa miundo ya fidia inayoanzia bure hadi inayohitaji leseni hadi ugawanaji wa mapato.",
  "schema-invalid": "schema si sahihi",
  "schema-valid": "schema sahihi",
  "site guide for AI systems": "mwongozo wa tovuti kwa mifumo ya AI",
  "summarization — summaries, with or without attribution": "summarization — muhtasari, kwa au bila utambulisho wa chanzo",
  "this site’s AI content rights policy": "sera ya haki za maudhui ya AI ya tovuti hii",
  "this site’s license catalog": "katalogi ya leseni ya tovuti hii",
  "training / fine_tuning / distillation — model internalization tiers": "training / fine_tuning / distillation — ngazi za uingizaji ndani wa modeli",
  "training — model training and fine-tuning permission": "training — ruhusa ya mafunzo na kurekebisha modeli",
  "transformation — structured extraction and derivative works": "transformation — uchukuaji uliopangwa na kazi zinazotokana nazo",
  "undeclared — high-risk pipelines may exclude": "undeclared — mitiririko yenye hatari kubwa inaweza kuondoa",
  "verbatim_memory — whether exact reproduction is permitted": "verbatim_memory — iwapo uzalishaji sahihi wa maneno umeruhusiwa",
  "versioned, citable, traceable": "yenye toleo, inayoweza kunukuliwa, inayoweza kufuatiliwa",
  "“AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer” now published in English as the canonical edition; the Chinese original manuscript remains available and both versions cross-link.": "\"AICL: Tabaka la Uchukuaji na Uwezo wa AI\" sasa imechapishwa kwa Kiingereza kama toleo rasmi; muswada asili wa Kichina unabaki kupatikana na matoleo yote mawili yanaunganishwa.",
  "“Protocolized Openness” confirmed as an English-language paper (with Chinese parallel passages) — no separate translation planned.": "\"Uwazi wa Kiitifaki\" imethibitishwa kuwa waraka wa lugha ya Kiingereza (wenye vifungu sambamba vya Kichina) — hakuna tafsiri tofauti iliyopangwa.",
  "↑ live machine-readable policy of this site": "↑ sera ya moja kwa moja inayosomeka na mashine ya tovuti hii",
